{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778904008493,"sessionID":"ses_1d10fb151ffec2BZrFWYyNH7va","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"functions.bash:16","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"git add src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo && git commit -m \"Fix logical definition of squamous epithelium\n\nChanged the logical definition of UBERON:0006914 'squamous epithelium'\nfrom:\n  intersection_of: has_part CL:0000076 ! squamous epithelial cell\nto:\n  intersection_of: composed_primarily_of CL:0000076 ! squamous epithelial cell\n\nThis ensures that only epithelia primarily composed of squamous epithelial\ncells are classified as squamous epithelium, rather than any epithelium\ncontaining at least one such cell. This aligns with the text definition\nand anatomical usage.\n\nCloses #3473\n\nSigned-off-by: @dragon-ai-agent\"","description":"Commit changes locally"},"output":"[scribe-v1-ai4curation-uberon-agent-config-v3-.-togetherai-moonshotai-Kimi-K2.6-iter1-issue-3473 123866f] Fix logical definition of squamous epithelium\n 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)\n","metadata":{"output":"[scribe-v1-ai4curation-uberon-agent-config-v3-.-togetherai-moonshotai-Kimi-K2.6-iter1-issue-3473 123866f] Fix logical definition of squamous epithelium\n 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)\n","exit":0,"description":"Commit changes locally","truncated":false},"title":"Commit changes locally","time":{"start":1778904008489,"end":1778904008492}},"id":"prt_e2ef0febe001ciTRgRFmlb0RTN","sessionID":"ses_1d10fb151ffec2BZrFWYyNH7va","messageID":"msg_e2ef0f575001vJxY9fz5S1f2ME"}}
