{"type":"text","timestamp":1778904019872,"sessionID":"ses_1d10fb151ffec2BZrFWYyNH7va","part":{"id":"prt_e2ef12ce9001szp3GXlYifhbBx","messageID":"msg_e2ef128d1001TNO79frDmI6uyN","sessionID":"ses_1d10fb151ffec2BZrFWYyNH7va","type":"text","text":"Done. I have:\n\n1. **Fixed the logical definition** of **squamous epithelium** (`UBERON:0006914`) by changing the equivalence axiom from `has_part some squamous epithelial cell` to `composed_primarily_of some squamous epithelial cell` in `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo`.\n2. **Added a `term_tracker_item`** linking back to issue #3473.\n3. **Committed the change locally** on the existing branch with a descriptive, signed commit message.\n4. **Created `ISSUE_COMMENTS.md`** and **`PR_COMMENTS.md`** in the repository root describing the change and rationale, without committing them.","time":{"start":1778904018153,"end":1778904019871}}}
